        {
          "html": "<div style=\"--color-midnight-ink:#050505;--color-ghost-white:#fdfdfd;--color-parchment:#e5e5e5;--color-slate-mist:#d4d4d4;--color-graphite:#151515;--color-deep-ash:#2f2f2f;--color-stone-gray:#a3a3a3;--color-cadet-grey:#737373;--color-cool-violet:#1500ff;--font-savee-font:'Inter',sans-serif;background:var(--color-midnight-ink);padding:48px 40px;width:600px;box-sizing:border-box;font-family:var(--font-savee-font);\"><p style=\"font-family:var(--font-savee-font);font-size:13px;font-weight:400;color:var(--color-cadet-grey);letter-spacing:0.015em;line-height:1.38;margin:0 0 24px 0;text-transform:uppercase;\">Features</p><h2 style=\"font-family:var(--font-savee-font);font-size:36px;font-weight:500;color:var(--color-ghost-white);letter-spacing:-0.02em;line-height:0.96;margin:0 0 48px 0;\">Save what moves you.</h2><div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:16px;\"><div style=\"background:var(--color-graphite);border-radius:14px;padding:28px;border:1px solid var(--color-deep-ash);display:flex;gap:20px;align-items:flex-start;\"><div style=\"width:40px;height:40px;background:var(--color-cool-violet);border-radius:9999px;flex-shrink:0;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;\"><svg width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M19 21l-7-5-7 5V5a2 2 0 012-2h10a2 2 0 012 2z\" stroke=\"#fdfdfd\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></div><div><p style=\"font-family:var(--font-savee-font);font-size:18px;font-weight:500;color:var(--color-ghost-white);letter-spacing:-0.01em;line-height:1.23;margin:0 0 8px 0;\">Save anything</p><p style=\"font-family:var(--font-savee-font);font-size:14px;font-weight:400;color:var(--color-stone-gray);letter-spacing:0.01em;line-height:1.5;margin:0;\">Images, colors, layouts, type — if it inspires you, save it. One click from anywhere on the web.</p></div></div><div style=\"background:var(--color-graphite);border-radius:14px;padding:28px;border:1px solid var(--color-deep-ash);display:flex;gap:20px;align-items:flex-start;\"><div style=\"width:40px;height:40px;background:var(--color-deep-ash);border-radius:9999px;flex-shrink:0;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;\"><svg width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\" stroke=\"#fdfdfd\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><path d=\"M12 6v6l4 2\" stroke=\"#fdfdfd\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></div><div><p style=\"font-family:var(--font-savee-font);font-size:18px;font-weight:500;color:var(--color-ghost-white);letter-spacing:-0.01em;line-height:1.23;margin:0 0 8px 0;\">No algorithm, ever</p><p style=\"font-family:var(--font-savee-font);font-size:14px;font-weight:400;color:var(--color-stone-gray);letter-spacing:0.01em;line-height:1.5;margin:0;\">Your feed is yours. No one decides what's relevant — only you. Pure inspiration, zero noise.</p></div></div><div style=\"background:var(--color-graphite);border-radius:14px;padding:28px;border:1px solid var(--color-deep-ash);display:flex;gap:20px;align-items:flex-start;\"><div style=\"width:40px;height:40px;background:var(--color-deep-ash);border-radius:9999px;flex-shrink:0;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;\"><svg width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M17 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H5a4 4 0 00-4 4v2\" stroke=\"#fdfdfd\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"7\" r=\"4\" stroke=\"#fdfdfd\" stroke-width=\"2\"/><path d=\"M23 21v-2a4 4 0 00-3-3.87M16 3.13a4 4 0 010 7.75\" stroke=\"#fdfdfd\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></div><div><p style=\"font-family:var(--font-savee-font);font-size:18px;font-weight:500;color:var(--color-ghost-white);letter-spacing:-0.01em;line-height:1.23;margin:0 0 8px 0;